bpCmId[i][1] = '\<p\>A great series of photographs, although lacks some variety. The first and last pictures are basically the same. Scenes of township kids playing soccer are nice and all, but there is much more happening across SA as we prepare to host this major event. Host cities are transforming, many new stadia are under development (http://www.capetown.gov.za/en/2010/gallery/Pages/StadiumConstructionProgress27.aspx), transport infrastructure is undergoing a major upgrade, not to mention all the preparations happening behind the scenes. Next time...\<\/p\>'
bpCmId[i][2] = 'coda'
bpCmId[i][3] = 'June 24, 2009 05:16 PM'
i++;
</script>



	
